fields.description: The file extension used to create the files. Type: string (or Expression with resultType string).
fields.name: FileExtension

fields.description: Specifies the file name pattern <fileNamePrefix>_<fileIndex>.<fileExtension> when copy from non-file based store without partitionOptions. Type: string (or Expression with resultType string).
fields.name: FileNamePrefix

fields.description: Limit the written file's row count to be smaller than or equal to the specified count. Type: integer (or Expression with resultType integer).
fields.name: MaxRowsPerFile

fields.description: Indicates whether string values should always be enclosed with quotes. Type: boolean (or Expression with resultType boolean).
fields.name: QuoteAllText
